---
title: French Onion Soup Burger with Béchamel, Caramelized Onions, and Kale Chips
description: "Who doesn’t love a burger? This dish is inspired by the classic French onion soup I ate as a child in France, but with an American twist. The blending of two cultures. A rich hearty burger topped with cheese and onions, simple to prepare but so rich and satisfying. This award winning burger will be an instant classic in your home. " - Chef Paul
